    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s still got plenty of life left in it? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it's honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape, runs super smooth, and has been really well-taken care of over the years. It's perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend adventures! I'd love for it to go to a great new home, so come on over and take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re really going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
