    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double-VANOS system. This example utilizes the Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing direct tactile feedback through the drivetrain. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced to address chassis fatigue, and the VANOS hub has been serviced to ensure timing precision. The suspension maintains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup delivers the intended lateral grip. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals remain sharp, with a linear power band and an aggressive 8,000 RPM redline. A turn-key performance icon for the technical driver.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
