    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been my pride and joy, maintained with a level of care that shows the moment you step inside. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the leather seats remain supple with only light natural creasing, and every button, dial, and screen functions exactly as it did on day one. Mechanically, it is in excellent health. I have followed the manufacturer\u2019s service schedule religiously, including a recent oil change and a full brake inspection. The tires have roughly 70% tread remaining, and the engine runs smoothly without any odd noises or leaks. This is a dependable, well-documented car that balances performance with everyday practicality. It\u2019s ready for its next owner to drive away with total peace of mind.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
